Product:UHJvZHVjdDoyOTE3NQ==.name: Greenies Teenie Dental Dog Treats
Product:UHJvZHVjdDoyOTE3NQ==.description: Support your furry sidekick’s dental health with Greenies Teenie Dental Dog Treats! These delicious original flavor dental dog treats are crafted with an irresistibly chewy texture that helps remove plaque and tartar. These natural dog treats are vet recommended for at-home oral health care because they help promote oral hygiene, freshen breath and contain highly soluble ingredients that are safe and easy for your pup to digest. Plus, you can feel extra confident knowing that these whisker-licking treats promote your canine companion’s overall health with vitamins, minerals and other nutrients! These treats are paw-fect for toy breeds and dogs between 5 and 15 lbs.

Feed 1 GREENIES™ Dental Treat per day. For dogs 5 - 15 lbs. Not suitable for dogs less than 5 lbs, or dogs less than 6 months of age. Fresh drinking water should always be available. ATTENTION: As with any edible product, monitor your dog to ensure the treat is adequately chewed. Gulping any item can be harmful or even fatal to a dog. For each GREENIES™ dental treat fed, reduce your dog’s main meal by 26 kcal. 

**Choose the Right Size for Your Dog**

* TEENIE® Treats: 5 - 15 lbs
* Petite: 15 - 25 lbs
* Regular: 25 - 50 lbs
* Large: 50 - 100 lbs

keyBenefits: Natural dog treats crafted with vitamins, minerals and other nutrients.
Features a unique texture that cleans down to the gumline, fights plaque and tartar and promotes fresh breath!
These veterinarian-recommended dog treats are accepted by the VOHC (Veterinary Oral Health Council.)
These goodies are crafted with a whisker-licking taste!
Proudly crafted in USA facilities with quality ingredients from around the world.
cautions: As with any edible product, monitor your dog to ensure the treat is adequately chewed. Gulping any item can be harmful or even fatal to a dog.

itemSubHeader.richText: Treat your cat or dog to clean teeth and fresh breath with Greenies Dental Treats. These delicious treats help fight plaque and tartar and are vet-recommended for at-home dental care. Made with natural ingredients that are easy to digest, Greenies Dental Treats come in both cat and dog formulas in a variety of flavors and sizes to suit every type and breed of furry friend.

The soft, chewy texture and distinctive grooves of Greenies Dental Treats for Dogs are helpful for maintaining healthy teeth and gums. The unique texture helps gently scrape away plaque and tartar, which also helps freshen your dog’s breath. They provide an easy way to help maintain your dog’s dental health without having to struggle with a traditional toothbrush. Plus, your dog will love every bite!

Greenies believes in the value of preventive care, so they’ve assembled a team of scientists, vets and nutritionists to design quality treats and supplements that help your pet live a healthier life. Greenies products make it fun to do what’s best for your pet, whether that’s maintaining dental health, administering pills, supporting joints or improving the skin and coat. With their irresistible taste and health benefits, innovative Greenies products help you become the hero of treat time.
